{"tid":1482253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武警深圳演練 梁愛詩:可能是為慶祝國慶匯演","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:09:57.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"610d131bc2d2934a06d74d4b2b1d522040557b70","tid":1482253,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190818113333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190818113333&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=9bd83b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190818113333</a><br />\n<br />\n   基本法委員會前副主任、 前律政司司長梁愛詩表示, 特區政府必要時可向中央請求駐軍幫助維持社會秩序, 但駐軍進入香港也要遵守駐軍法和香港法例, 因此即使出動解放軍, 亦不等於一國兩制完結.<br />\n        梁愛詩在一個電台節目上指, 現時香港的情況未到戰爭狀態要顛覆國家政權, 認為目前是社會治安問題多於國家統一安全問題, 未有需要要求解放軍出動.<br />\n        對於武警在深圳演練, 梁愛詩不認同是為了震懾香港市民, 亦不是跟近日示威活動有關, 認為可能是為慶祝國慶, 在全國進行武警匯"},{"pid":"2812399c9bb7c3ca29f7087db50a87d8fc9a1b24","tid":1482253,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a7ed574139a3fc9b942d02e5970b3b162ea69f","tid":1482253,"uid":92448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"精神勝利法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw, 佢幾時死"},{"pid":"de59bf55abadf71eebf98d322bf280be3f973a03","tid":1482253,"uid":139409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=e22b502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=e22b502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"b3dcdca8b906317390d8a1f29c54639b5a73209c","tid":1482253,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de59bf55abadf71eebf98d322bf280be3f973a03","tid":1482253,"uid":139409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=e22b502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗